name: Free Fall Fred
description:
The goal of Free Fall Fred is to dodge the obstacles falling from the top of the screen and collect the coins to score points. Collecting health packs will regen your health by one let me know your high score enjoy.

Controlls

left and right arrow keys or W and D to move
